,"quote":{"pid":"df22c90bdedc7718f52f26314870a9da3241271b","tid":1308241,"uid":28257,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:38:18.000Z","msg":"刑事，因為係刑事，只有政府可以入稟刑事告人。殺人被捕，其實唔係受害者告，係政府告。 聽落告或不告都係警方選擇"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:46:27.000Z","msg":"補充返<br />\n檢唔檢控係律政司決定嘅"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:02:39.000Z","msg":"唔可以私人民事檢控？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:10:03.000Z","msg":"FROM WIKI <a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%88%91%E4%BA%8B%E8%A8%B4%E8%A8%9F%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%2588%2591%25E4%25BA%258B%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E8%25A8%259F%25E7%25A8%258B%25E5%25BA%258F&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0GhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=f13e66ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%88%91%E4%BA%8B%E8%A8%B4%E8%A8%9F%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F</a><br />\n<br />\n刑事檢控權<br />\n法律上並沒有規定刑事檢控權只落在政府部門身上，亦即<span style=\"color: red;\">公眾或個人在原則上也有權作出私人刑事檢控</span>。而事實上，《裁判官條例》第14條的條款，是用作指示律政司司長如何介入私人檢控當中，更能清楚地反映了私人刑事檢控在法律理論上的可能性。可是現實上，由於檢控過程和司法過程中所涉及的高昂成本，和缺乏政府部門所擁有的調查案件的人力、資源和特權，再加上律政司所擁有介入和取代私人刑事檢控權，以及由無罪推定原則所延伸出來對證據均達到無合理疑點準則的要求，<span style=\"color: red;\">所以實際上，私人刑事檢控幾乎並不存在</span>。而官方的最終刑事檢控權則落在律政司身上，並不受任何人(包括特首)的干擾。事實上，這最終獨立刑事檢控權是《基本法》給予律政司的"},{"pid":"de0b739d05037135179a926ac18265499bcb26ef","tid":1308241,"uid":242059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:10:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f59aad6f584c8ba5b0e78420b0310fdf028fbd89","tid":1308241,"uid":197086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:13:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1ff81d17684d4207bbfe4384baf5ede6d65bc489","tid":1308241,"uid":258721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:13:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"11bcea9c411795f364afd56e334a78a121cfc5bf","tid":1308241,"uid":264915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:15:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />即係可以告班狗啦！"},{"pid":"b1e2b2333b0c2e25238f4315835efc3f30d21ba7","tid":1308241,"uid":124455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:16:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0655386e883908e3d7052f65009c0358500299da","tid":1308241,"uid":112231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:17:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"166b0d0526607be5db0dee714f7f7c4cc5a61bde","tid":1308241,"uid":14605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:18:24.000Z","msg":"仲講法律，玩撚完左啦"},{"pid":"f32c5e6caf387faee8fcf1f8015203d1d37fd66a","tid":1308241,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:18:41.000Z","msg":"咁貼係法律上有無權"},{"pid":"0ebe2f9adb37e3e341950107de029e5ae8040221","tid":1308241,"uid":12816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:19:30.000Z","msg":"警犬做野有法律可言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n法治係香港一早消失左"},{"pid":"7a26d993c0ffcd633783abe39f032a2a138ee228","tid":1308241,"uid":71393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:19:35.000Z","msg":"貼係民主黨個度咪得<br />\n其他地方佢地搵食環搞"},{"pid":"20da9226e9a738ebd11528628f3dbba8524e96c7","tid":1308241,"uid":107596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:20:12.000Z","msg":"琴晚長沙灣隻撕紙狗比人拉左啦"},{"pid":"ef49d37a2d835c9a2cccf5fbba00bb5d466d988f","tid":1308241,"uid":122752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:21:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"57105762d4d2e3a0716f1dfbf856b27eca3d352f","tid":1308241,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:21:16.000Z","msg":"[文宣] 中英聯合聲明超級懶人包 Video<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1308374\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1308374</a>"},{"pid":"cbf46ec618fb2b004d9e3ca59c749b4f839170f7","tid":1308241,"uid":215010,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0ca3dfed4b62a22528add96fe9a29cd736c0bcd4","tid":1308241,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:15:47.000Z","msg":"抄低班警犬牌<br />\n然後報案話佢地刑事毀壞<br />\n再唔係去小額錢債審裁處索償，得唔得㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=2326807284099209&amp;set=a.125153000931326&amp;type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D2326807284099209%26set%3Da.125153000931326%26type%3D3%26theater&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0GhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=11f779cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=2326807284099209&amp;set=a.125153000931326&amp;type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n黑警刑毀。真係以為自己獅子王？獅子狗就有你份<br />\n在貼紙並無違反其他法律的情況下，政府只獲香港法例第132章 《公眾衞生及市政條例》 第104C條所賦予一般性的「將招貼及海報移走的權力」。<span style=\"color: gold;\">然而，此法定權力只能由「主管當局」行使。根據《條例》第3(1)條，「主管當局」為《條例》附表3中指明的公職人員。就第104C條而言，第104E條將「主管當局」定為食物環境衛生署署長，而非警務處處長。警務人員並無享有上述「將招貼及海報移走的權力」。</span><br />\n<br />\n無論如何，第104C條賦予的並非獨立存在（free standing）的權力；<span style=\"color: gold;\">引用此法定權力的前提，是展示或張貼招貼及海報的行為本身違反第104A條。</span>[1]<br />\n<br />\n第104A條規定，在政府土地展示或張貼招貼或海報，須先得到主管當局書面准許。在Chee Fei Ming v Director of Food and Environmental Hygiene (No 2)[2] 一案中，高等法院原訟法庭法官林雲浩裁定，<span style=\"color: gold;\">當第104A條<em>用於管制靜態示威中所用的宣傳物品</em>時，該條文目前賦予政府的權力過分模糊（尤其是示威者根本無從得知如何以個人身份申請准許），無法滿足人權法中法律確定性的要求，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屬違反受憲法保障的言論及集會自由</span>。</span><br />\n<br />\n既然第104A條在示威自由面前屬違憲，依賴其法律效力的第104C條自然亦無法被合憲地執行。<br />\n假設警務人員嘗試引用上述「將招貼及海報移走的權力」，在此特定情況下不可能被視作正在執行職務，所以期間如<span style=\"color: gold;\">摧毀或損壞任何財產</span>，亦不可能被視作有任何合法辯解。<br />\n<br />\n#連儂牆咁和平都要搞<br />\n#是你教我和平遊行是沒用<br />\n<br />\n[1] 參見Chee Fei Ming v Director of Food and Environmental Hygiene [2016] 3 HKLRD 412 (CA) [57] per Lam VP。<br />\n[2] [2018] HKCFI 2031, [2018] 4 HKLRD 517。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:26:03.000Z","msg":"淨係睇104C同104E？有冇睇埋142？"},{"pid":"0de3458c3fb5af97799becbe2a5dbe9a55d74d91","tid":1308241,"uid":251207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:31:44.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"542cad22287d4d4fdb1dd6718e8fecbac5bcbdb2","tid":1308241,"uid":24948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:33:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ae9adcde5467eb4c445283aa6f227b375ed629fe","tid":1308241,"uid":266181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:34:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51d07545aa857a02907e3de474960cff0bcfc546","tid":1308241,"uid":31324,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"617f6ad8c5b56fbc6ff9bfc75220c5aaf10b749d","tid":1308241,"uid":28257,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"449e793b220f204a2a62bec801a57af1b079409f","tid":1308241,"uid":138409,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0da94c0826de177c473b9843e510e7dfede64d21","tid":1308241,"uid":28257,"like":146,"dislike":1,"score":145,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:23:21.000Z","msg":"唔係法律人，亦有請法律人解釋<br />\n<br />\n係長沙灣，警察捉左個道友兼告埋佢，咁落得一次CHARGE，如果唔係次次都捉同入刑事毀壞，咁會變歧視，選擇性執法，可唔可以入稟民事告警署。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:29:54.000Z","msg":"民事？定司法覆核啊？始終依家係懷疑行政當局行使權力失當<br />\n<br />\n不過JR都要錢，而且相當耐<br />\n可能又要搵郭生<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:36:08.000Z","msg":"我指搣紙/被捕一方(當然係藍絲，入唔入稟佢地的事)，由上得知，警察係唔可以搣，咁藍絲搣，如果下次警察唔捉人，算唔算徇私，選擇性執法? 算唔算違反警察操守?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:36:38.000Z","msg":"Fb 都流傳緊幾個妹妹撕左藍絲係連儂既 poster..<br />\n仲出埋樣<br />\n大家引用法例要小心誤中"},{"pid":"b9bdaf337437841a1ea8f462c5576ff055031e6b","tid":1308241,"uid":77302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT